# Vidly
## Docker - project(react - node - mongodb)




## Installation

```dgr
first install docker - docker-compose
git clone form my repo
cd projct
docker-compose up || docker-compose up -d
go to browser => localhost:3000 # web view
go to browser => localhost:3001/api # api
go to browser => localhost:3001/api/movies # api/movies 
```

For production environments...

```sh
install docker-machine AND Add Env as (Driver - token - URL - ...).
conneting to host with Secure Shell (SSH).
... etc.
```
